-- Miranda to Focus on Production at Sesikhona as Urgency to List Coal Fades
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-10-25T06:05:29Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/miranda-to-focus-on-production-at-sesikhona-as-urgency-to-list-coal-fades.html
Miranda Mineral Holdings Ltd. said
the urgency to separately list the shares of its coal unit has
“dissipated somewhat” and the company’s immediate focus will
be bringing Sesikhona to production.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
